both. And the same thing for their flipper length as well. So we have these three data frames. You

00:15:02.739 --> 00:15:06.659
can perhaps imagine a situation where different people have collected these data.

00:15:09.219 --> 00:15:15.460
Now, one-to-many relationships, things work out pretty nicely. I have my three penguins data frame

